{"id":534496,"magazine_id":48707,"template_id":41,"title":"Een dag bij...","alias":"een-dag-bij-2018-1","page_no":7,"meta_keywords":null,"meta_description":"AmerZine editie 1, Voorjaar 2018. Het digitale magazine van Amerpoort. \nSamen werken aan een goed leven voor mensen met een verstandelijke beperking.","share_url":null,"options":{"has_disabled_header":false,"exclude_from_navigationbar":false,"share_url":null},"header":null,"content":{"background":{"filename":"achtergrond_dag_van.472727280e29.jpg","uri":"\/images\/achtergrond_dag_van.472727280e29.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":284241,"width":1600,"height":1067},"nav_type":"bars","sidebar":1,"image":{"filename":"0001_20180221-amerpoort-109.d4325c09337e.jpg","uri":"\/images\/0001_20180221-amerpoort-109.d4325c09337e.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":607670,"width":1600,"height":1067},"title":"EEN DAG BIJ...","subtitle":"De Keerkring","description":"<p>een dagbesteding op locatie Nieuwenoord voor jong en oud met een ernstig verstandelijke beperking en Moeilijk Verstaanbaar Gedrag.<\/p><p><br><\/p><p>Op <a href=\"https:\/\/www.amerpoort.nl\/locaties\/overdag\/de-keerkring.html\" onclick=\"Magazine.tracker.trackOutbound( this, event, 'click', $(this).text() );\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">onze website&nbsp;<\/a>vindt u meer informatie over deze locatie.<\/p>","text_align":"left","header_space":"0","item":[{"title":null,"subtitle":null,"description":null,"item":[{"image":{"filename":"0003_20180221-amerpoort.ab3f5a681382.jpg","uri":"\/images\/0003_20180221-amerpoort.ab3f5a681382.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":330418,"width":1600,"height":1067},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>Deze vissen gaan overal mee naartoe. Trots laat Annemieke&nbsp;haar vissen zien aan begeleider Marloes en Denzel.<\/p>"},{"image":{"filename":"0004_20180221-amerpoort-62.45108d60a10f.jpg","uri":"\/images\/0004_20180221-amerpoort-62.45108d60a10f.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":294579,"width":1600,"height":1067},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>Omar kwam vandaag gespannen binnen. Nadat hij Marloes een klap heeft gegeven, wordt hij even in bedwang gehouden. Dit helpt om even opnieuw de dag te starten.<\/p>"},{"image":{"filename":"0006_20180221-amerpoort-23.e1eb5a8ba2f8.jpg","uri":"\/images\/0006_20180221-amerpoort-23.e1eb5a8ba2f8.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":569175,"width":1600,"height":1062},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>Niels krijgt 1-op-1 begeleiding. Bewegen is belangrijk. Op zijn skelter rijdt hij over het terrein van Nieuwenoord.<\/p>"},{"image":{"filename":"0007_20180221-amerpoort-28.0ebe8513616b.jpg","uri":"\/images\/0007_20180221-amerpoort-28.0ebe8513616b.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":457560,"width":1600,"height":1067},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>Na het skelteren&nbsp;gaat Niels aan de slag met evenwichtsoefeningen op de balk.<\/p>"},{"image":{"filename":"0021_20180221-amerpoort-43.9bc46e8970f0.jpg","uri":"\/images\/0021_20180221-amerpoort-43.9bc46e8970f0.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":279242,"width":1600,"height":1067},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>En dan is het tijd om uit te rusten in de snoezelruimte. Niels luistert vandaag naar ABBA (Super Trouper) en de Beatles.<\/p>"},{"image":{"filename":"0008_20180221-amerpoort-5.3592be06f553.jpg","uri":"\/images\/0008_20180221-amerpoort-5.3592be06f553.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":412987,"width":1600,"height":1067},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>De groep is veel buiten te vinden,&nbsp;in de tuin is genoeg te doen.<\/p>"},{"image":{"filename":"0009_20180221-amerpoort-8.c8c63707b800.jpg","uri":"\/images\/0009_20180221-amerpoort-8.c8c63707b800.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":250472,"width":1600,"height":1067},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>Chris&nbsp;zoekt even contact met Marloes.<\/p>"},{"image":{"filename":"0010_20180221-amerpoort-97.41a961b22073.jpg","uri":"\/images\/0010_20180221-amerpoort-97.41a961b22073.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":276397,"width":1600,"height":1067},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>Na het buitenspelen is het eerst tijd om de handen wassen.<\/p>"},{"image":{"filename":"0011_20180221-amerpoort-36.a12ec46c3562.jpg","uri":"\/images\/0011_20180221-amerpoort-36.a12ec46c3562.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":309071,"width":1600,"height":1067},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>De muziektherapeuten komen langs. Chris&nbsp;speelt piano samen met Ingrid.<\/p>"},{"image":{"filename":"0012_20180221-amerpoort-35.22f60cb9d914.jpg","uri":"\/images\/0012_20180221-amerpoort-35.22f60cb9d914.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":399403,"width":1600,"height":1067},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>Muziektherapeut Margien is ondertussen met Annemieke aan het trommelen. Denzel trommelt mee op zijn benen.&nbsp;<\/p>"},{"image":{"filename":"0013_20180221-amerpoort-64.49683cb2beb2.jpg","uri":"\/images\/0013_20180221-amerpoort-64.49683cb2beb2.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":278086,"width":1600,"height":1067},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>Denzel trommelt nog even door als de muziektherapeuten vertrokken zijn. Ondertussen is het tijd om te verschonen.<\/p>"},{"image":{"filename":"0015_20180221-amerpoort-51.83838541b97a.jpg","uri":"\/images\/0015_20180221-amerpoort-51.83838541b97a.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":566964,"width":1600,"height":1067},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>De keerkring is vaak buiten te vinden. Wandelen is om meerdere redenen belangrijk. Bijvoorbeeld om prikkels te reguleren, of om zintuigen aan het werk te zetten of om te leren om te gaan met je groepsgenoten.<\/p>"},{"image":{"filename":"0016_20180221-amerpoort-55.443c772534c8.jpg","uri":"\/images\/0016_20180221-amerpoort-55.443c772534c8.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":359166,"width":1600,"height":1021},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>Naar de winkel om boodschappen te doen voor de lunch. Ook dit is een activiteit waar cli\u00ebnten veel van leren. Annemieke mag soms&nbsp;alleen naar de winkel.<\/p>"},{"image":{"filename":"0018_20180221-amerpoort-69.4af02fd65114.jpg","uri":"\/images\/0018_20180221-amerpoort-69.4af02fd65114.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":274405,"width":1600,"height":1067},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>Lunchen! Denk niet dat de groep gezellig tafelt. De meeste cli\u00ebnten zijn in 10 minuten wel klaar met eten en gaan dan weer van tafel.<\/p>"},{"image":{"filename":"0023_20180221-amerpoort-101.633399d0cdf5.jpg","uri":"\/images\/0023_20180221-amerpoort-101.633399d0cdf5.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":424486,"width":1600,"height":1069},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>Gelukkig heeft de groep wel genoeg rust voor een mooi groepsportret! Dank voor het inkijkje in jullie dag!<\/p>"}],"style":{"title":["color: ;","color: ;"],"subtitle":["color: ;","color: ;"],"paragraph":["color: ;","color: ;"]}}],"padding":null}}